race.description: Cadillac Racing (N/P) Tg 1-4W Series H Pr2 Divisio
race.comment: KIA KEEPING (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.82 beating Magic Poppy. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to go well again. CLOSE SHAVE (8) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 400m behind Mister Cadillac (23.41) in a OPEN. Was in the money the start prior. Won at his only start from this box. Can figure in the finish. COMPTON LIZZIE (5) hit the frame last time at Gawler but the start prior rocketed around 400m at this track in 23.10. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. TRADING HALT (2) racing over this distance brings the best out in her.
